videos.headline: Ole Miss strikes 1st
videos.description: John Rhys Plumlee connects with Scottie Phillips for a 21-yard touchdown and 7-0 Ole Miss lead.

videos.headline: Badie races to end zone for Missouri TD
videos.description: Kelly Bryant finds Tyler Badie who goes down the sideline for a 17-yard score and 9-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Badie races to end zone for Missouri TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rountree bolts for 41-yard TD
videos.description: Missouri goes up 18-7 when Larry Rountree III takes off for a 41-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Downing stretches for 54-yard TD
videos.description: Dawson Downing just reaches the end zone on a 54-yard touchdown, and after review Missouri goes up 28-7.
